<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Milestone Celebration</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
            padding: 50px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            color: #ffffff;
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 48px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #333333;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .achievement {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffecd2 0%, #fcb69f 100%);
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .achievement-number {
            font-size: 64px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #d84315;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #999999;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #667eea;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>
                <%= emoji %>
            </h1>
            <h2 style="color: white; margin-top: 10px;">Milestone Unlocked!</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h2>Incredible work, <%= name %>!</h2>

            <div class="achievement">
                <p class="achievement-number">
                    <%= postCount %>
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; color: #d84315; margin: 10px 0 0 0;">Posts Created!</p>
            </div>

            <p>You've just reached a major milestone - <strong>
                    <%= postCount %> posts
                </strong>! This is a testament to your commitment to building your LinkedIn presence.</p>

            <p><strong>Here's what this means:</strong></p>
            <ul style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li>You're in the top 5% of LinkedIn content creators</li>
                <li>Your consistency is building your personal brand</li>
                <li>You're establishing yourself as a thought leader</li>
                <li>Your network is growing with every post</li>
            </ul>

            <div
                style="background-color: #e8f5e9; border-left: 4px solid #4caf50; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 30px 0;">
                <strong style="color: #2e7d32;">ðŸ“Š Impact Stats:</strong>
                <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; color: #2e7d32;">Content creators who post <%= postCount %>+ times see 10x
                        more profile views and 5x more opportunities than those who don't post consistently. You're on
                        the right path!</p>
            </div>

            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
                <a href="<%= process.env.FRONTEND_URL || 'http://localhost:3000' %>/dashboard/analytics"
                    class="cta-button">
                    View Your Analytics â†’
                </a>
            </div>

            <p><strong>Keep the momentum going:</strong></p>
            <ul style="color: #666666; line-height: 1.8;">
                <li>Maintain your posting schedule</li>
                <li>Engage with your audience's comments</li>
                <li>Experiment with different content formats</li>
                <li>Track what resonates with your audience</li>
            </ul>

            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">We're proud to be part of your LinkedIn journey!</p>

            <p style="margin-top: 20px;">Onwards and upwards!<br><strong>The LinkedInPulse Team</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= currentYear %> LinkedInPulse. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <a href="<%= preferencesUrl %>">Email Preferences</a> |
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">Unsubscribe</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>